name: Eduboard
tag_list: online-learning, online-tutoring, homework-help-service, online-test-prep, online-whiteboard, online-learning-community, education
overview:
Eduboard.com is an online comfortable tutoring, homework help and test prep service.

Eduboard.com connects students to tutors online and in real-time to work one-to-one on classes, homework or test preparation; the service is available 24 hours a day. At the very moment, more than 35 academic and career subjects are available at Eduboard.com and their guidance is ensured by a number of highly qualified and expert undergraduates, teachers, Profs and other professionals in the field to deliver the most qualitative tutoring from US and Canada.

Technologies

The design of Eduboard platform is based on sound pedagogical foundations that aim to help students learn the material quickly and effectively. Eduboard software solution represents smart ‘whiteboard’ technologies
